description:
Amendment covers the following areas: 
1) extended scope of services (airfreight and road) has been added for 4 business units: Research Shipping (ED Business support); CMC shipping; Corporate Facilities and Clinical Innovation Center (CLINiC); 
2) GxP and non- GxP Courier services has been added to the contract for Novo Nordisk end- users and prices for courier services;
3) Rate cards for 4 business units has been added as well

The Purpose of this agreement is twofold:
1) Update agreement for RTU caps according to revised project scope, additional requirements, sustainability activities, and revised capacities;
2) Update agreement for 2024 and 2025 prices for bulk caps based on predefined model and based on realised assumption of SCC and introduction of Laminazione as 2nd source of aluminium.
